<td colspan="3"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Book'; font-size: 300%;"> BYU-Idaho Alumni Ambassadors</span><span style="font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Book'; font-size: x-large;"><br /> The Eyes and Ears of BYU-Idaho and the Alumni Association </span> </strong></td>
</tr>
